<p>Last night Alex took care of me. There was a rotten apple in my emotional basket and she patiently and encouragingly helped me remove it.</p>

<p>To care for someone is to notice the little details of their current emotional and physical state, what is in balance and what is out of balance, to see them more clearly than they see themselves, and to help them move toward a more high quality energy in their mind and body.</p>

